Create fillets on tagged paths.



```js
fillet(data: FilletData, extrude_group: ExtrudeGroup) -> ExtrudeGroup
```

### Examples

```js
const part001 = startSketchOn('XY')
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> line([0, 10], %, "thing")
  |> line([10, 0], %)
  |> line([0, -10], %, "thing2")
  |> close(%)
  |> extrude(10, %)
  |> fillet({ radius: 2, tags: ["thing", "thing2"] }, %)
```
